title: JUL 1 2022 - LIBERAL WORLD ORDER: BIDEN REGIME PLUNGES AMERICA INTO RECESSION
description:
The lovely and ever-so-thoughtful Biden administration has decided to begin fourth of July celebrations early by sending us straight into a recession! In their kindness, they have announced that there are going to be flight delays over the weekend. Next, the supreme court term has ended, and Jack Posobiec breaks down the rulings and what they mean for this country. And four men have been charged in connection to the the disturbing border incident where 53 migrants were found dead in a trailer.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
